At the same time, the lack of fossil resources will need to be faced in order to continue to generate electricity, while not forgetting the necessary need to reduce greenhouse gas emissions in order to combat climate change, a subject currently disappearing from environmental debates.
An accident in Fukushima has no effect on any of these parameters.
